options: To evaluate model performance on unseen data

set5.question: What is the primary goal of Explainable AI (XAI)?
options: To make AI decisions interpretable and transparent

options: Computing at the edge of networks
Processing data closer to where it's generated

options: To compare performance of different approaches

options: Artificially generated data that mimics real data

options: It can lead to unfair or discriminatory outcomes
